With Christmas around the corner, people have already started looking for that perfect gift to give to their loved ones. Look no further because the Headway Natal Westville Christmas Craft Market has just the perfect ideal gift for you. Pop in on 30 November at 11 Menston Road from 9am to 1pm to find what you are looking for. There will be lots of items on offer from crafts, beadwork, jams, pickles, Christmas cakes, toys and so much more. “Our charity shop will also be open as well as a tea garden and a white elephant shop. All items on sale are made by Headway Members,” said Headway Natal’s manager Colleen